1) Using the program should be intuitive and similar to code6.html sample 
   (Buttons at bottom for selecting objects. Keys for moving objects).
2) Objects can be moved using keys specified in the lab instruction.
3) For the arms F key is for closing the arm, B key is for opening the arms.
4) Bonus task: added a Start Animation button to play a short animation.
   For best effect, reset the scene before play.
5) Tested in Safari 10.